灵活运用整句（如排比、对偶）与散句的结合，使文章气势贯通又不失活泼自然。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-eapudvd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-eapudvd","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-mc9na1k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-mc9na1k","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"巧用问句推进逻辑与情感"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：适度且精准地加入设问与反问句。"}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-m30p2rt","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-m30p2rt","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-vyb3kf7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vyb3kf7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-h77uwr7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-h77uwr7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"设问"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：用于段落开头或转折处，通过自问自答引发阅卷者思考，自然引出下文的深层剖析；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-rmlasr3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rmlasr3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-t8udsbu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-t8udsbu","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"反问"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：用于论证高潮或结尾升华时，以无疑而问的强烈语气增强文章的论辩色彩与感染力，直击人心。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-xhk4fc5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xhk4fc5","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3gaslh4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3gaslh4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"善用修辞增添底蕴"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：巧妙运用比喻、引用、化用古诗词等手法，避免辞藻堆砌，力求语言的精准与文学性。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-nutjxky","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nutjxky","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-les4piy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-les4piy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"规避AI痕迹"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-9uz718b","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9uz718b","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3ftay3z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3ftay3z","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-iwb9mhx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-iwb9mhx","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"严禁"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用空洞的排比句堆砌（如“梦想是……梦想是……”）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-3ogleqp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3ogleqp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-dv87rsg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dv87rsg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"严禁"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用“综上所述”、“总而言之”、“随着时代的发展”等刻板的AI常用过渡词。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-38hxr88","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-38hxr88","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-r5wybf1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-r5wybf1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"允许表达中有轻微的个性化跳跃或情感化的重复强调，使文章更具“人味”和真情实感。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-7agac1e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7agac1e","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-5kq2saj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5kq2saj","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"思维与论证（核心技法）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"     ："}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-g0l372y","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-g0l372y","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-5078ebw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5078ebw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-r2rlxz4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-r2rlxz4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"必备论式组合"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：优先使用下列方法中的两种及以上，根据文章需要自然融入，避免刻意拼装。"}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-pmjiob3","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-pmjiob3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-26n4dwu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-26n4dwu","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ji0x0e0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ji0x0e0","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分解论证（拉升与钻洞）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"     ：证明分论点时，注意分论点间的层递关系。可采用“拉升式”（由底层肉身/物质体验升华到高层灵魂/生存层面）或“钻洞式”（由表层社会现象深入挖掘背后的文化基因或心理动因）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-sc5cb3j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-sc5cb3j","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-5cowbwy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5cowbwy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"举例论证（典型事例）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"     ：选取古今中外典型人物或时事热点，通过具体故事来支撑论点，做到叙议结合，拒绝单纯堆砌素材。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-rqb7q7k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rqb7q7k","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-euiehvy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-euiehvy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"归谬论证（反向推导）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"     ：先提出与论点相反的假定，推导出荒谬或不可接受的后果，从而有力地反证原论点的正确性，增强说服力。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-pjf3npz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-pjf3npz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-v3g2n56","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-v3g2n56","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"辅助论式拓展"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：可适当穿插使用道理/引证论证（引用经典著作、名人警句）、类比论证（通过相似事物比较类推）或反证法，丰富文章的论证维度。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-iax145w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-iax145w","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-feed9on","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-feed9on","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"隐性植入辩证法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：将辩证法的三大规律(对立同一、量变质变、否定之否定)内化为文章的底层逻辑，但"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"严禁直接出现"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“对立统一”、“量变质变”、“否定之否定”等哲学术语。具体操作如下："}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-yggao42","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yggao42","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-4y91v5m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-4y91v5m","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ip2l1a1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ip2l1a1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"体现矛盾转化"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：分析事物内部的矛盾双方（如危与机、强与弱），阐述它们在特定条件下如何相互依存并向对立面转化。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ry0ylkj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ry0ylkj","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-roanko1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-roanko1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"体现积累与飞跃"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：论述从微小的积累到质的突破的过程，强调厚积薄发的重要性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-1bmjhs7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-1bmjhs7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-p40p3bz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-p40p3bz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"体现螺旋上升"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：展现事物发展不是简单的循环，而是看似回归原点实则境界提升的曲折前进过程。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-rat4g01","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rat4g01","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-1s9wgqm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-1s9wgqm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"论据要充分且鲜活，拒绝陈词滥调（避免过度使用司马迁、李白、爱迪生等老套素材）。结合时事热点、历史文化等多维度素材。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ljym003","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Ni4=","Num":6},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ljym003","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-uwtm6fg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-uwtm6fg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心素材优先库："}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-reh5pji","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-reh5pji","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-yr327g5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yr327g5","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-wn0gbxi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wn0gbxi","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"钱伟长（中国力学之父）：必须作为核心论据或升华点。重点使用其“九一八事变后，物理仅15分的他毅然弃文从理，只为‘科学救国’”的转折。体现“个人命运与国家命运的同频共振”，以此替换老旧的“范仲淹”、“岳飞”等素材。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ps5f60b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ps5f60b","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-y76f5jb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-y76f5jb","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"西西弗斯（加缪笔下的荒诞英雄）：必须作为核心意象。重点描写他推石上山的徒劳与坚持，引用“登上顶峰的斗争本身足以充实人的心灵”。用以论证“在无意义的生活中构建意义”、“过程即意义”，以此替换老旧的“海伦·凯勒”、“张海迪”等素材。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ze7bp5f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Ny4=","Num":7},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ze7bp5f","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-28w2sec","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-28w2sec","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"古典底蕴与化用："}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-h0abyd8","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-h0abyd8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-6q4pzqa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-6q4pzqa","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-920ai20","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-920ai20","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"至少自然嵌入2–3条下面提供的的典故、文章(不必引用原文，文章总结、提炼亦可)、诗词名句、电影，并保证与论证逻辑紧密相关。在保证与论证逻辑紧密相关的情况下，优先使用标记为(优先)的条目。"}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-qbkqxcf","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qbkqxcf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ffemjkp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ffemjkp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-k5a4hih","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-k5a4hih","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《尚书》五福：寿、福、康宁、攸好德、考终命(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-acywqb2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-acywqb2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-0ydhu6h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0ydhu6h","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"鲁迅：无穷的远方，无数的人们，都与我相关。(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-9jotnrg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9jotnrg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-0c4hjnz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0c4hjnz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗曼·罗兰：世界上只有一种英雄主义，就是在认清生活的真相之后依然热爱生活。(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-kmjvpik","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kmjvpik","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-br7eh9i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-br7eh9i","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"特鲁多医生墓志铭：医生有时治愈，常常帮助，总是安慰。(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-lrhm7hf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lrhm7hf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-5k2p13p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5k2p13p","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗素：参差多态乃是人类幸福的本源。(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-6eiizn3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-6eiizn3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-mqo7ic3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-mqo7ic3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：每一个不曾起舞的日子都是对生命的辜负。(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-rhnpe8c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rhnpe8c","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-kquju1v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kquju1v","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"独学而无友，则孤陋而寡闻。(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-bbjrvvh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bbjrvvh","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-8nkqxq1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8nkqxq1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"蓬生麻中，不扶而直。(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-r6rrxj6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-r6rrxj6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-5ti7avs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5ti7avs","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"投之亡地然后存，陷之死地然后生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-7pxregi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7pxregi","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3fohpyc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3fohpyc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏不逾日，罚不还面。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-zdpv5fv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-zdpv5fv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-048iamn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-048iamn","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"路遥《平凡的世界》当一个人集中地凝视着自己的不幸时，他就很难想象别人的苦难。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-w3map16","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-w3map16","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-tkmv6vb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-tkmv6vb","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小敌之坚，大敌之擒也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5ep3fta","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5ep3fta","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-nr369x8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nr369x8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小人肥口，君子肥身。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-o2xz5c0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-o2xz5c0","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-yiqb1na","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yiqb1na","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我生本无乡，心安是归处。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-bgs8uk7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bgs8uk7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-r0lzsxo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-r0lzsxo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陈独秀：青春如初春，如朝日，如百卉之萌动，如利刃之新发于硎(xíng)，人生最宝贵之时期也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-b3gw8as","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-b3gw8as","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-r7y1k2x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-r7y1k2x","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"舒婷《致橡树》：我们分担寒潮、风雷、霹雳；我们共享雾霭流岚、虹霓。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-l9ojo44","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-l9ojo44","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-gosh4om","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-gosh4om","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《美丽心灵》约翰·纳什"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-cme7av6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-cme7av6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-rjk6ztf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rjk6ztf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"西格里夫·萨松：心有猛虎，细嗅蔷薇。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-s9axf5y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-s9axf5y","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-uzoapsb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-uzoapsb","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：大胆的见解就好比下棋时移动一个棋子，它可能被吃掉，但它却是胜局的起点。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-8w9obdx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8w9obdx","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ppxxwjp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ppxxwjp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：西西弗斯无声的全部快乐就在于：他的命运是属于他的，他的岩石是他的事情。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-dpunabn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dpunabn","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-isdoztm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-isdoztm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：在隆冬，我终于知道，我身上有一个不可战胜的夏天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-y5m7tr2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-y5m7tr2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-29hztsf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-29hztsf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海明威：一个人可以被毁灭，但不能被打败。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-qr77p6d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qr77p6d","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-hpbjkl8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hpbjkl8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杨绛：生活一半是柴米油盐，一半是星辰大海。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-in2dcyo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-in2dcyo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-a2bl97e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-a2bl97e","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"昭昭若日月之明，离离如星辰之行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-c3vwmw3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-c3vwmw3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qily3z3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qily3z3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"事以急败，思因缓得。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-irwq5f6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-irwq5f6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qd8xyjy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qd8xyjy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"晚来风定钓丝闲，上下是新月。千里水天一色，看孤鸿明灭。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5oyubve","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5oyubve","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-gyhxgz2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-gyhxgz2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老舍《骆驼祥子》：经验是生活的肥料，有什么样的经验便变成什么样的人，在沙漠里养不出牡丹来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-574b87p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-574b87p","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-yfqe4k8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yfqe4k8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"黄金累千，不如一贤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-hba3n32","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hba3n32","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-choas1m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-choas1m","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：理论是灰色的，唯生命之树常青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-6k4r7lm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-6k4r7lm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-8u3z7pz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8u3z7pz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道不同，不相为谋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-92afjl0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-92afjl0","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-o8rn1hv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-o8rn1hv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"浴不必江海，要之去垢；马不必骐骥，要之善走。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-yziayzz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yziayzz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ip0dzk1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ip0dzk1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苟利于民不必法古，苟周于事不必循旧。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-cwn2li2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-cwn2li2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-pvchbrn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-pvchbrn","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"怀重宝者，不以夜行；任大功者，不以轻敌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-oycnyf7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-oycnyf7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-0zmyszw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0zmyszw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"独行穿落叶，闲坐数流萤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-rg39nzo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rg39nzo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-rmfvtg7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rmfvtg7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"佯北勿从，锐卒勿攻，饵兵勿食。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-g4q3jyd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-g4q3jyd","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ai07p82","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ai07p82","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：只有流过血的手指，才能弹出世间的绝唱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-en55ol4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-en55ol4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-lbatwnl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lbatwnl","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《蛤蟆先生去看心理医生》：没有一种批判比自我批判更强烈，也没有一个法官比我们自己更严苛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-sjtbc3u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-sjtbc3u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-joe3kfa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-joe3kfa","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"德不孤，必有邻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-jamk6bz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-jamk6bz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-a01urjx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-a01urjx","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"吹灭读书灯，一身都是月。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-j37379d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-j37379d","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-hbvk73u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hbvk73u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古今之成大事业、大学问者，必经过三种之境界：“昨夜西风凋碧树，独上高楼，望尽天涯路”，此第一境也；“衣带渐宽终不悔，为伊消得人憔悴”，此第二境也；“众里寻他千百度，蓦然回首，那人却在灯火阑珊处”，此第三境也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-hwpx3q5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hwpx3q5","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-pzffrx0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-pzffrx0","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"勿以身贵而贱人，勿以独见而违众。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-urqeo97","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-urqeo97","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-55g6hq9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-55g6hq9","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山河虽无恙，吾辈当自强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-r9q9lwq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-r9q9lwq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-6cldc03","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-6cldc03","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君埋泉下泥销骨，我寄人间雪满头。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-cep89ha","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-cep89ha","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-mmiv3bg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-mmiv3bg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"蛇蛇硕言，出自口矣。巧言如簧，颜之厚矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-idqm9pz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-idqm9pz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-e8t11iq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e8t11iq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良剑期乎断，不期乎镆铘；良马期乎千里，不期乎骥骜(jì ào)。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-1kapr2q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-1kapr2q","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3ctvjrn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3ctvjrn","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"勤能补拙，学可医愚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-tkduz1w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-tkduz1w","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-bryoncj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bryoncj","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"男儿何不带吴钩，收取关山五十州。请君暂上凌烟阁，若个书生万户侯？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-wh8uhfy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wh8uhfy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-puengts","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-puengts","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为政不难，不得罪于巨室。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-j6skqf9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-j6skqf9","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-wf9knvd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wf9knvd","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"长恨人心不如水，等闲平地起波澜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-0pd0g8z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0pd0g8z","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-gm2bwcs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-gm2bwcs","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"试玉要烧三日满，辨材须待七年期。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-0sane3h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0sane3h","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-7y5xmow","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7y5xmow","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"清风一枕南窗卧，闲阅床头几卷书。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-dh1trtm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dh1trtm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qripqpg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qripqpg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不知而自以为知，百祸之宗也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ed4sdwb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ed4sdwb","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-iiu0xah","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-iiu0xah","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"轻财足以聚人，律己足以服人，量宽足以得人，身先足以率人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-jy24hf3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-jy24hf3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ynlbro7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ynlbro7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百战百胜，不如一忍。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-u6lehpk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-u6lehpk","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-546mqvg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-546mqvg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"功名半纸，风雪千山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-nsaoc3u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nsaoc3u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-fhtpfhf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-fhtpfhf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"井以甘竭，李以苦成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-nvztj3h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nvztj3h","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-hycoz0c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hycoz0c","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赠君明月满前溪，直到西湖畔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-4nduvve","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-4nduvve","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-rjbs3bp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rjbs3bp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道虽迩(ěr)，不行不至；事虽小，不为不成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-gwqi4tf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-gwqi4tf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ptgewcv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ptgewcv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为草当作兰，为木当作松。兰秋香风远，松寒不改容。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-qhsncvw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qhsncvw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-zr4w9k6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-zr4w9k6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用威者不轻怒，善用恩者不妄施。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-yfn92q3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yfn92q3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-kkdohr0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kkdohr0","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马先驯而后求良，人先信而后求能。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-hn7ux14","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hn7ux14","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-m2ix2ua","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-m2ix2ua","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"形象水，水之形，避高而趋下，兵之形，避实而击虚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-qhajuno","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qhajuno","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-bi4sdb0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bi4sdb0","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人要是不能从过程中体味幸福和快乐，生命就成了一场荒诞的苦役。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-vjk6j7z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vjk6j7z","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-4wig9xy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-4wig9xy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君王城上竖降旗，妾在深宫那得知？十四万人齐解甲，更无一个是男儿！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-fwu2ny0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-fwu2ny0","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-tha35ep","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-tha35ep","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者，避其锐气，击其惰归，此治气者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-gw1wm8k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-gw1wm8k","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-w6gdq6t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-w6gdq6t","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"政入万山围子里，一山放出一山拦。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ggd9wsu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ggd9wsu","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ppnm81h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ppnm81h","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地者万物之逆旅也；光阴者百代之过客也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-y5k9k0u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-y5k9k0u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-u9rz3wy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-u9rz3wy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虽不能至，心向往之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-x1mp10z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-x1mp10z","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-y2yh1zo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-y2yh1zo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"高者未必贤，下者未必愚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-knyhpph","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-knyhpph","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-uvys7de","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-uvys7de","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"与朋友交游，须将他们好处留心学来，方能受益；对圣贤言语，必要我平时照样行去，才算读书。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-d02w13m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-d02w13m","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-dr2f45m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dr2f45m","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"二人同心，其利断金；同心之言，其臭(xiù)如兰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-378kgr7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-378kgr7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-xfj2zdh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xfj2zdh","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子不蔽人之美，不言人之恶。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-7f1hn9m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7f1hn9m","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-mr0uokg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-mr0uokg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知者不怨人，知命者不怨天；怨人者穷，怨天者无志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-e77539n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e77539n","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-wquan4e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wquan4e","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道德用于自律时好过一切法律，用于律他时坏过一切私刑！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-48nih7a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-48nih7a","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-gju1ixy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-gju1ixy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山高自有客行路，水深自有渡船人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-rhor93m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rhor93m","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-dnht3lf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dnht3lf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"攻人以谋不以力，用兵斗智不斗多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-32v4m1b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-32v4m1b","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-z24hcu4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-z24hcu4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不忘初心，方得始终。初心易得，始终难守。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-lo3yxln","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lo3yxln","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-hfavgav","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hfavgav","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不迁怒，不贰过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-jatyz6h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-jatyz6h","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-xy2gz3x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xy2gz3x","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用兵之法，十则围之，五则攻之，倍则分之，敌则能战之，少则能逃之，不若则能避之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-8117dhn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8117dhn","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-pcckyvl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-pcckyvl","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"越自尊大，越见器小。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-7hywm5d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7hywm5d","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-t1bv5t2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-t1bv5t2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"浮云一别后，流水十年间。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5obrorz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5obrorz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-xjnh1pg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xjnh1pg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穆勒 ：个人的自由，以不侵犯他人的自由为自由。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-yo23e5a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yo23e5a","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-j7u44jv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-j7u44jv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小舟从此逝，江海寄余生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5k0yw6z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5k0yw6z","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-g1c5j5x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-g1c5j5x","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"云山苍苍，江水泱泱，先生之风，山高水长！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-kfhwz68","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kfhwz68","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3dxzx7f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3dxzx7f","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"行远道者假于车，济江海者因于舟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-mcbgawe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-mcbgawe","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-h77wu8l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-h77wu8l","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一花独放不是春，百花齐放春满园。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-7350yl3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7350yl3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-0ri61j3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0ri61j3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"立志欲坚不欲锐，成功在久不在速。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-nz1a6fr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nz1a6fr","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-dpg8am1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dpg8am1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏不逾日，罚不还面。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5ca2889","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5ca2889","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-k9284iv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-k9284iv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"布伦南：手头上有点钱的人认为爱是世界上最重要的东西，而穷人则明白世界上最重要的是金钱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-fb441u9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-fb441u9","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-2mfrrpd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2mfrrpd","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"冯至《十四行集》：我们准备着，深深地领受，那些意想不到的奇迹。在漫长的岁月里，忽然有彗星的出现，狂风乍起。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-3jxhh44","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3jxhh44","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3wppy1q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3wppy1q","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"疾风怒雨，禽鸟戚戚；霁月光风，草木欣欣。天地不可一日无和气，人心不可一日无喜神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-m61zj8g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-m61zj8g","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ax2uc3d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ax2uc3d","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫之高华，只在于道德气节。鄙夫之炫耀，但求诸服饰起居。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-sm8hqcb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-sm8hqcb","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-tkuu0e3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-tkuu0e3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"甘井近竭，招木近伐。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-7lqt071","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7lqt071","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-5u6tb9u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5u6tb9u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者，屈人之兵而非战也，拔人之城而非攻也，毁人之国而非久也，必以全争于天下。故兵不顿而利可全，此谋攻之法也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-wpwak0q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wpwak0q","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-6yg6mde","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-6yg6mde","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你吞并一切，像远方，像大海，像时间。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-kc2jggx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kc2jggx","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-pbsphuh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-pbsphuh","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"挟取笔端风雨，快写胸中丘壑，不肯下樊笼。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-7li1j1i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7li1j1i","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-m66x5hk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-m66x5hk","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"巴尔扎克：一星陨落，黯淡不了星空灿烂；一花凋零，荒芜不了整个春天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-whmopg8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-whmopg8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-4iw6pcm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-4iw6pcm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"伯修斯：在所有不幸中，最不幸的事是曾经幸福过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-iy8vorg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-iy8vorg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-rc1xren","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rc1xren","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草萤有耀终非火，荷露虽团岂是珠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-e88sj5c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e88sj5c","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-egsbgvo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-egsbgvo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"耳闻之不如目见之，目见之不如足践之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-kc2d3ja","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kc2d3ja","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-24qb3c1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-24qb3c1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"卖花担上，买得一枝春欲放。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-9vua85h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9vua85h","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-2nngr8e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2nngr8e","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"亭亭山上松，瑟(sè)瑟谷中风。风声一何盛，松枝一何劲。冰霜正惨凄，终岁常端正。岂不罹(lí)凝寒，松柏有本性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-1lim2iz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-1lim2iz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-tntpd3d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-tntpd3d","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好问则裕，自用则小。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-9l9cxhc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9l9cxhc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-bokyhvy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bokyhvy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雾失楼台，月迷津渡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-l9ixi7j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-l9ixi7j","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-736wcqy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-736wcqy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：世界以痛吻我，我也要报之以歌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-hji407g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hji407g","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-46jkqxx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-46jkqxx","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"千人之诺诺，不如一士之谔谔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-xzltoj9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xzltoj9","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-hwtoikx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hwtoikx","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"早岁读书无甚解，晚年省事有奇功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-xe37fpa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xe37fpa","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-hh4gt73","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hh4gt73","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你所浪费的今天，是昨天死去的人奢望的明天；你所厌恶的现在，是未来的你回不去的曾经。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-w0iyy6f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-w0iyy6f","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-h1hqd0t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-h1hqd0t","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：有很多人常常抱怨没有机会，其实没有机会本身亦是一个机会：一个锻炼自己耐力和充分积蓄自己力量的机会。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-bey8lbg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bey8lbg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ugsri6u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ugsri6u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"世界让我遍体鳞伤，但伤口长出的却是翅膀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-vrb9vth","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vrb9vth","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-fqzzkaq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-fqzzkaq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凡战者，以正合，以奇胜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-91tkwhj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-91tkwhj","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-egu0i1z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-egu0i1z","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方其中，圆其外。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-0o3bz52","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0o3bz52","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-uezjbai","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-uezjbai","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：苦难既然把我推到了悬崖的边缘，那么就让我在这悬崖的边缘坐下来，顺便看看悬崖下的流岚雾霭，唱支歌给你听。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-s8p4m2n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-s8p4m2n","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-4mgrqmk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-4mgrqmk","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"国虽大，好战必亡；天下虽安，忘战必危。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-mz255qo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-mz255qo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-a7sk2nn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-a7sk2nn","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：每个冬天的句号都是春暖花开。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-4voduxl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-4voduxl","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-din849o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-din849o","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百里趋利，兵家所忌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-vl099lf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vl099lf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-rl8bmot","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rl8bmot","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李大钊：谁对时间越吝啬，时间对谁越慷慨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-0giapv7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0giapv7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-eb9olcd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-eb9olcd","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"粗缯大布裹生涯，腹有诗书气自华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-w1pxj0p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-w1pxj0p","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-gvibqam","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-gvibqam","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"夫未战而庙算胜者，得算多也；未战而庙算不胜者，得算少也。多算胜，少算不胜，而况于无算乎？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-09p4uji","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-09p4uji","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-cottzjs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-cottzjs","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"慈不掌兵，情不立事，义不理财，善不为官。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-nifwmpm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nifwmpm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-q8l636t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-q8l636t","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大巧在所不为，大智在所不虑。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-r3g8tcl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-r3g8tcl","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-4teq2j4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-4teq2j4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海到尽头天作岸，山登绝顶我为峰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-2u9n0as","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2u9n0as","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-my7kcxz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-my7kcxz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨之为物，能令昼短，能令夜长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-vab79oy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vab79oy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-jcjsowa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-jcjsowa","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善出奇者，无穷如天地，不竭如江海。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5du9v5u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5du9v5u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-21x1a8r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-21x1a8r","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大丈夫行事，当磊磊落落，如日月皎然。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-kehinud","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kehinud","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-7bzf475","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7bzf475","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知者行之始，行者知之成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-lseap3u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lseap3u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-yfu1vh7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yfu1vh7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者不以短击长，而以长击短。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-lz4yk87","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lz4yk87","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qekbbuq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qekbbuq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"振衣千仞冈，濯足万里流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-vfj4er9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vfj4er9","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-oy2or1g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-oy2or1g","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：你今天受的苦、吃的亏、担的责、扛的罪、忍的痛，到最后都会变成光，照亮你的路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-jiojxnp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-jiojxnp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-f08f7ui","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-f08f7ui","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"张而不弛，文武弗能也；弛而不张，文武弗为也。一张一弛，文武之道也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-hkh6zxz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hkh6zxz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-zybbjnc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-zybbjnc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善为士者，不武；善战者，不怒；善胜敌者，不与；善用人者，为之下。是谓不争之德，是谓用人之力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-of8xw4m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-of8xw4m","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-sc2ixo5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-sc2ixo5","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"中心藏之，何日忘之！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ogo1grc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ogo1grc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-pgvb5br","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-pgvb5br","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：没有比脚更长的路，没有比人更高的山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-gq1h6me","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-gq1h6me","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-vs9ocsf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vs9ocsf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：才能是在寂静中造就，而品格则是在世间汹涌波涛中形成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-jcpolpt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-jcpolpt","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-u5eo0x3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-u5eo0x3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我有迷魂招不得，雄鸡一声天下白。少年心事当拏云，谁念幽寒坐呜呃。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5bynz7y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5bynz7y","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-mxzi9oc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-mxzi9oc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尺之木必有节目，寸之玉必有瑕疵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-f8s3v6r","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-f8s3v6r","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-wjj979b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wjj979b","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"曾国藩：天下古今之庸人，皆以一惰字致败；天下古今之才人，皆以一傲字致败。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-zbspbbo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-zbspbbo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ngtbta5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ngtbta5","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"培根：当你孤独寂寞时，阅读可以消遣。当你高谈阔论时，知识可供装饰。当你处世行事时，正确运用知识意味着力量。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-l75rw9g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-l75rw9g","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-2w8623c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2w8623c","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"辅车相依，唇亡齿寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-eum05te","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-eum05te","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3vdrqhf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3vdrqhf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"池田大作：荣誉有如萤虫之火，在黑暗的夜空里，它放着光，显示出美丽，极其可贵。但是靠近一看，立刻就会明白它是何等的软弱无力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-i6if1pt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-i6if1pt","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-epka449","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-epka449","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：谁终将声震人间，必长久深自缄默；谁终将点燃闪电，必长久如云漂泊。我的时代还没有到来，有的人死后方生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-s662svx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-s662svx","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-5zpaj9l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5zpaj9l","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"三毛：梦想，可以天花乱坠；理想，是我们一步一个脚印踩出来的坎坷道路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-a0slhae","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-a0slhae","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-u465n33","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-u465n33","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志不可一日坠，心不可一日放。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-q9sqqhc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-q9sqqhc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-axv3foo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-axv3foo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一双冷眼看世人，满腔热血酬知己。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-l4k65d2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-l4k65d2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-l4c26dg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-l4c26dg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗翔：误解是人生常态，理解是稀缺的例外。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-u8fctgw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-u8fctgw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3hwrk9e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3hwrk9e","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杀人亦有限，列国自有疆。苟能制侵陵，岂在多杀伤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-g8ls1uw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-g8ls1uw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-c3k7qie","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-c3k7qie","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朝闻道，夕死可矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-p0qf7tt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-p0qf7tt","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-kfonjtm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kfonjtm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫四方志，安可辞固穷。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-oyl0fso","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-oyl0fso","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-241rj82","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-241rj82","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"粪虫至秽变为蝉，而饮露于秋风；腐草无光化为荧，而耀采于夏月。故知洁常自污出，明每从暗生也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-c0bmqe6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-c0bmqe6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-q92hq5c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-q92hq5c","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"物以稀为贵，情因老更慈。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ze3h2ml","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ze3h2ml","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-m3anmk6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-m3anmk6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不可积，过不可长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-lxwgpr4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lxwgpr4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-bnvoqxe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bnvoqxe","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不能受谏，安能谏人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-0u1iw9u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0u1iw9u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qqcnaiz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qqcnaiz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生岂草木，寒暑移此心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-py44puj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-py44puj","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-nkrsa7m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nkrsa7m","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大丈夫当容人，勿为人所容。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ebzkuls","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ebzkuls","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-bnwvtxh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bnwvtxh","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不为无益之事，何以悦有涯之生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-8180ec8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8180ec8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-v8fh0pv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-v8fh0pv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海棠未雨，梨花先雪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-onxpxzd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-onxpxzd","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ia67qfv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ia67qfv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"地薄者大木不产，水浅者大鱼不游。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-p4x7w9m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-p4x7w9m","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-81c6jes","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-81c6jes","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"忧勤是美德，太苦则无以适性怡情；淡泊是高风，太枯则无以济人利物。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-y0wmsxn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-y0wmsxn","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-mwyx7bq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-mwyx7bq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读书为身上之用，而人以为纸上之用。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-u5swetj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-u5swetj","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-w80h98p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-w80h98p","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天可补，海可填，南山可移。日月既往，不可复追。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5zp776z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5zp776z","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-p9rlm6t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-p9rlm6t","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼布尔：请赐予我平静，去接受我无法改变的；给予我勇气，去改变我能改变的；赐我智慧，分辨这两者的区别。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-f2hkgs0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-f2hkgs0","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-npw7ggs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-npw7ggs","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"腹中贮书一万卷，不肯低头在草莽。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-a8agmiq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-a8agmiq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-7ct3ali","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7ct3ali","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"须知少日拏云志，曾许人间第一流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-78mhww9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-78mhww9","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-w8zm5wd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-w8zm5wd","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间的步伐有三种：未来姗姗来迟，现在像箭一样飞逝，过去永远静立不动。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-t24a1kd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-t24a1kd","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-8x6vqvt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8x6vqvt","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天若无雪霜，青松不如草。地若无山川，何人重平道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-lh3nw2m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lh3nw2m","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-6l0vjxp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-6l0vjxp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凡心所向，素履所往，生如逆旅，一苇以航。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-cxn6x5u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-cxn6x5u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-s5pxmux","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-s5pxmux","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"缓事宜急干，敏则有功；急事宜缓办，忙则多错。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-zibfim4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-zibfim4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-6ke7056","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-6ke7056","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"众口铄金，积毁销骨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-kg213rj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kg213rj","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-8nzbujw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8nzbujw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"春日迟迟，卉木萋萋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ael2089","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ael2089","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-k96lkaj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-k96lkaj","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"若有恒何必三更眠五更起，最无益莫过一日曝十日寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-e3a9mf7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e3a9mf7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-bncekxp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bncekxp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百战百胜，非善之善者也；不战而屈人之兵，善之善者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-v3tyvje","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-v3tyvje","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-slyoryp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-slyoryp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人之相知，贵相知心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-hx23qk7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hx23qk7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-9fam3yx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9fam3yx","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"桃李春风一杯酒，江湖夜雨十年灯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-e3ezfjj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e3ezfjj","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-226yt0i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-226yt0i","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"东风知我欲山行，吹断檐间积雨声。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-dbb9h20","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dbb9h20","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-8w0agzc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8w0agzc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"桐花万里丹山路，雏凤清于老凤声。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-vg7hbb8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vg7hbb8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-5yty8i3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5yty8i3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生不能设计，你只能面对。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-u609a4d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-u609a4d","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-8yb6x3s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8yb6x3s","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地不仁，以万物为刍狗；圣人不仁，以百姓为刍狗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-8udm71s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8udm71s","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ysdejkg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ysdejkg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"心随长风去，吹散万里云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-m0vebrq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-m0vebrq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-bvgk91q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bvgk91q","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"见面怜清瘦，呼儿问苦辛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-guyi235","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-guyi235","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-z9bfyga","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-z9bfyga","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"查尔斯·A·比尔德：当天空黑暗到一定程度，星辰就会熠熠生辉。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-95cgkyc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-95cgkyc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-hjr9j6p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hjr9j6p","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪中何以赠君别，惟有青青松树枝。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-w12cdlh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-w12cdlh","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-hgz98z5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hgz98z5","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏必加于有功，刑必断于有罪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-iiexdfo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-iiexdfo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-9dj3210","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9dj3210","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"规小节者不能成荣名，恶小耻者不能立大功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-9ctxegq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9ctxegq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-yro9xno","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yro9xno","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"沈从文：聪明人要理解生活，愚蠢人要习惯生活。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-72bj8pk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-72bj8pk","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qebaw7x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qebaw7x","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"康德：世界上有两件东西能震撼人们的心灵：一件是我们心中崇高的道德标准；另一件是我们头顶上灿烂的星空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-etfq8eb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-etfq8eb","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-j61bk2l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-j61bk2l","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"叔本华：财富就像海水，饮得越多，渴得越厉害。名望实际上也是如此。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-4igq93b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-4igq93b","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3xa8ylg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3xa8ylg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵者，国之大事，死生之地，存亡之道，不可不察也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-x2fqv8q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-x2fqv8q","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-i6uab1g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-i6uab1g","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵无常势，水无常形，能因敌变化而取胜者，谓之神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-x1piymy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-x1piymy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3v0fu4p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3v0fu4p","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何物动人二月杏花八月桂，有谁催我三更灯火五更鸡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-oqb6r2x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-oqb6r2x","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-midx6ml","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-midx6ml","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自古骄兵多致败，从来轻敌少成功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-1zkn823","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-1zkn823","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-1c2qfb7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-1c2qfb7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知往日所往之非，则学日进矣；见世人可取者多，则德日进矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-oy9gmgk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-oy9gmgk","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-msfkycb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-msfkycb","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马太福音：凡有的，还要加倍给他，叫他有余；没有的，连他剩余的也要夺过来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-e9v1ci9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e9v1ci9","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-xv8vxvp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xv8vxvp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"风流不在谈锋胜，袖手无言味最长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-6utu99x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-6utu99x","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-b2l5wl4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-b2l5wl4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"恻隐之心，人皆有之；羞恶之心，人皆有之；恭敬之心，人皆有之；是非之心，人皆有之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-hedwvez","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hedwvez","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qfffuw3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qfffuw3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"攻人以谋不以力，用兵斗智不斗多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-cc21j0h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-cc21j0h","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-p6qdpf1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-p6qdpf1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"已识乾坤大，犹怜草木青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-d289iv3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-d289iv3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-7yl3kz9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7yl3kz9","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"鹏北海，凤朝阳。又携书剑路茫茫。明年此日青云上，却笑人间举子忙。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-g0x6gcv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-g0x6gcv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-bmod3fw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bmod3fw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朝饮木兰之坠露兮，夕餐秋菊之落英。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-efvkn0e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-efvkn0e","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-weo9zta","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-weo9zta","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"千人同心则得千人之力，万人异心则无一人之用。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-yhvif5y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yhvif5y","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-vj82ug6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vj82ug6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"出其所不趋，趋其所不意。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-bw9su45","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bw9su45","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-t7dzrgq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-t7dzrgq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"戒骄风清月朗，除躁海阔天空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-i3lc0cc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-i3lc0cc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-pmmho56","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-pmmho56","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何时杖尔看南雪，我与梅花两白头。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ls64oik","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ls64oik","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-q7u2zt4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-q7u2zt4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一时宠利有尽，千秋青史难欺。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-0hj1mak","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0hj1mak","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-nfjqqfb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nfjqqfb","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山川异域，风月同天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-uxz8apt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-uxz8apt","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-5zce2ja","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5zce2ja","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"白石似玉，奸佞似贤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-81wdtba","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-81wdtba","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-h6leewc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-h6leewc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"深厚的教养所集成的勇猛，远远胜过无知无情者的鲁莽。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-etv5r0s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-etv5r0s","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-p44gilk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-p44gilk","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"积财千万，不如薄技在身。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-q2ugv9c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-q2ugv9c","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-jk8ntef","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-jk8ntef","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海明威：生活总是让我们遍体鳞伤，但到后来，那些受伤的地方一定会变成我们最强壮的地方。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-wc5kr0u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wc5kr0u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-oqebfnn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-oqebfnn","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当年不肯嫁春风，无端却被秋风误。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-eggalgn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-eggalgn","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-8ee1p6s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8ee1p6s","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良辰美景奈何天，赏心乐事谁家院。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-wgtcjfy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wgtcjfy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-24ta7rg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-24ta7rg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"唤起一天明月，照我满怀冰雪，浩荡百川流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-1cozbab","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-1cozbab","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-x6a1kwz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-x6a1kwz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"休对故人思故国，且将新火试新茶。诗酒趁年华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-lss0ib1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lss0ib1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-sn1woon","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-sn1woon","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：那些听不见音乐的人，认为那些跳舞的人疯了。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-isq2id6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-isq2id6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-93mydvx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-93mydvx","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：其实人跟树是一样的，越是向往高处的阳光，它的根就越要伸向黑暗的地底。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-p5ifode","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-p5ifode","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-wfuj5wr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wfuj5wr","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"玉可碎而不可改其白，竹可焚而不可毁其节。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-jh4rae2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-jh4rae2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-hc8yj8y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hc8yj8y","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"南风吹其心，摇摇为谁吐？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-nkgfmp2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nkgfmp2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-wyby8a5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wyby8a5","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"巴金：希望是人生之需要。人如没有希望，何异江河干涸了流水？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-txk11lw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-txk11lw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-dd5dsk8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dd5dsk8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穷不失义，达不离道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-vxlsuxb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vxlsuxb","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-rie9avg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rie9avg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为者常成，行者常至。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-3xjx24t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3xjx24t","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-20mrh78","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-20mrh78","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"青云当自致，何必求知音？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-4of4hvk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-4of4hvk","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-xu1rej0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xu1rej0","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"争名者于朝，争利者于市。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-xxptdrp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xxptdrp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-er9rwto","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-er9rwto","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天上浮云如白衣，斯须变幻如苍狗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-epzvil4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-epzvil4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-og34z9e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-og34z9e","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"莺花犹怕春光老，岂可教人枉度春？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5bxwpe2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5bxwpe2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ztpael3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ztpael3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生芳秽有千载，世上荣枯无百年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-dpgr2q8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dpgr2q8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-38krgvo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-38krgvo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当你的欢乐和悲哀变大的时候，世界就变小了。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-z025vow","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-z025vow","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-i93ihvi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-i93ihvi","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故将有五危，必死可杀，必生可虏，忿速可侮，廉洁可辱，爱民可烦。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-98apzhm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-98apzhm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-2nrhwlc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2nrhwlc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"纵使文章惊海内，纸上苍生而已。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5mwdi5u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5mwdi5u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-uwuq9zv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-uwuq9zv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"死生契阔，与子成说。执子之手，与子偕老。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-kzu7f3n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kzu7f3n","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-1ynwxnv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-1ynwxnv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兼听则明，偏信则暗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-jrrodz3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-jrrodz3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-yowjora","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yowjora","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"弃燕雀小志，作鸿鹄高翔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-6v5op7f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-6v5op7f","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-om0zd46","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-om0zd46","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"眼界要阔，遍历名山大川；度量要宏，熟读五经诸史。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-om7lk37","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-om7lk37","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-fnkek5c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-fnkek5c","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地存肝胆，江山阅鬓华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-bddgwvw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bddgwvw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-xzvlhne","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xzvlhne","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生不相见，动如参与商。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-sclwxup","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-sclwxup","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-0tc3f7p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0tc3f7p","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"莫道君行早，更有早行人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-txfl2vm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-txfl2vm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-kk0wi8w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kk0wi8w","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大人者，不失其赤子之心者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-49u7ddu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-49u7ddu","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ygv1cfo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ygv1cfo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"英雄者，胸怀大志，腹有良谋，有包藏宇宙之机，吞吐天地之志者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-xterc2z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xterc2z","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-k9585sp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-k9585sp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪里温柔，水边明秀，不借春工力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-83ocfr1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-83ocfr1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-x7h0ba4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-x7h0ba4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良言一句三冬暖，恶语伤人六月寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-1nr09bz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-1nr09bz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-geoqex2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-geoqex2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学如弓弩，才如箭镞。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-25csu0a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-25csu0a","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-w0t7gu1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-w0t7gu1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人不读书，其犹夜行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-cdhx9xd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-cdhx9xd","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-nl2vg6j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nl2vg6j","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穷猿奔林，岂暇择木！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-r2rw7xs","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-r2rw7xs","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-d8tpnf3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-d8tpnf3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"令在必信，法在必行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-y84315x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-y84315x","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-92p5sor","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-92p5sor","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其疾如风，其徐如林，侵掠如火，不动如山，难知如阴，动如雷震。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-yd3ddko","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yd3ddko","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ic80nxh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ic80nxh","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天下熙熙，皆为利来；天下攘攘，皆为利往。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-vyyd5g0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vyyd5g0","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-j3vyw8y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-j3vyw8y","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我亦飘零久！十年来，深恩负尽，死生师友。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-1lu9llo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-1lu9llo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-t71iyni","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-t71iyni","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"板凳要坐十年冷，文章不写一句空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-o5zf55h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-o5zf55h","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-p88m99v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-p88m99v","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有心为善，虽善不赏；无心为恶，虽恶不罚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-cqixhmn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-cqixhmn","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-l168e0j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-l168e0j","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不目见口问，不能尽知也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-16nsbw2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-16nsbw2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-bcl784a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bcl784a","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一年之计，莫如树谷；十年之计，莫如树木；终身之计，莫如树人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-d3l1fsc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-d3l1fsc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-2yumfde","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2yumfde","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不因幸运而故步自封，不因厄运而一蹶不振。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ekq2auj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ekq2auj","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3zln4v3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3zln4v3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良弓难张，然可以及高入深；良马难乘，然可以任重致远。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-gsjqmmp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-gsjqmmp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-49xxolf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-49xxolf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上兵伐谋，其次伐交，其次伐兵，其下攻城。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-r5tbawu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-r5tbawu","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-z5bltu8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-z5bltu8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志合者不以山海为远，道乖者不以咫尺为近。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-iimq823","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-iimq823","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-bjmj98i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bjmj98i","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海水梦悠悠，君愁我亦愁。南风知我意，吹梦到西洲。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-k3tkk58","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-k3tkk58","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-lqytvms","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lqytvms","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不幸者常常愿意同幸运者相比，抱怨自己的运气。幸运者常常不愿同不幸者相比，相信自己的努力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-wbaxbp6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wbaxbp6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-1fbnuk4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-1fbnuk4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"怯生于勇，弱生于强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-l5r0gp5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-l5r0gp5","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-p5gd112","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-p5gd112","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贵上极则反贱，贱下极则反贵。贵出如粪土，贱取如珠玉。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-bwed7il","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bwed7il","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-t3owpds","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-t3owpds","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有志者事竟成破釜沉舟百二秦关终属楚，苦心人天不负卧薪尝胆三千越甲可吞吴。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-2l47nsg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2l47nsg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-7ejgwmt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7ejgwmt","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"昔日之得不足以自衿，今日之成不容以自限。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-wiwvfzu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wiwvfzu","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-dnuwhs8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dnuwhs8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不善操舟者，恶河之曲。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-i2a3mu6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-i2a3mu6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qw8xk8q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qw8xk8q","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"操千曲而后晓声，观千剑而后识器。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-f4m4p6r","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-f4m4p6r","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-fgatili","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-fgatili","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"长安何处在，只在马蹄下。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-3jedofe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3jedofe","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-zi4in07","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-zi4in07","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人情阅尽秋云厚，世事经多蜀道平。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-34hl559","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-34hl559","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-44nlej6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-44nlej6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志行万里者，不中道而辍足。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-2sfwe13","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2sfwe13","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-lussnd3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lussnd3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"交友须带三分侠气，做人要存一点素心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-vds6w47","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vds6w47","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-9yq8tbs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9yq8tbs","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"男儿不展风云志，空负天生八尺躯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-au5ntkq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-au5ntkq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-vizwank","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vizwank","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"愿作远方兽，步步比肩行。愿作深山木，枝枝连理生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-25kvy6u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-25kvy6u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-zed9tb2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-zed9tb2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵不厌诈，将贵知机。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-stv00nb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-stv00nb","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-nna8jrd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nna8jrd","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上士闻道，勤而行之；中士闻道，若存若亡；下士闻道，大笑之。不笑不足以为道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-rzpaj7x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rzpaj7x","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-xgs6484","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xgs6484","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子慎始，差若毫厘，缪以千里。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-o9rr1gg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-o9rr1gg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-938rflg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-938rflg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古来多被虚名误，宁负虚名身莫负。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-s2bwn0g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-s2bwn0g","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-fzyi4db","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-fzyi4db","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我志在寥阔，畴昔梦登天。摩挲素月，俯仰已千年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ytz1yoe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ytz1yoe","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-7amw60s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7amw60s","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们每个人出生的时候，并非是两手空空，而是捏了一张生命的借记卡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-gdfvkie","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-gdfvkie","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ky4opxs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ky4opxs","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好风凭借力，送我上青云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-apf6th1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-apf6th1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ygc8zpa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ygc8zpa","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"玉在山而草木润，渊生珠而崖不枯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-d1ijggw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-d1ijggw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-af531ke","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-af531ke","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学之染人，甚于丹青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-azm52j7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-azm52j7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-0uddni6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0uddni6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地有万古，此身不再得；人生只百年，此日最易过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-bhq9jqn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bhq9jqn","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-pa97spl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-pa97spl","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"十有九人堪白眼，百无一用是书生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-isof54a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-isof54a","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-haiqyx2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-haiqyx2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫志四海，万里犹比邻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-e5jm8td","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e5jm8td","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-l6qwcos","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-l6qwcos","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"仗义每多屠狗辈，负心多是读书人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-a3qba5w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-a3qba5w","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-okw1ivo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-okw1ivo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"涓涓不塞，将为江河。荧荧不救，炎炎奈何。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-2a5867g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2a5867g","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-eoqslkn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-eoqslkn","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生如寄，多忧何为？今我不乐，岁月如驰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-qlc41nh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qlc41nh","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-yg46vu6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yg46vu6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天行有常，不为尧存，不为桀亡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ad7eznr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ad7eznr","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-vw5owpr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vw5owpr","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读书志在圣贤，非徒科第；为官心存君国，岂计身家？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5x0c75u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5x0c75u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-8bu41a3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8bu41a3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"少而好学，如日出之阳；壮而好学，如日中之光；老而好学，如秉烛之明。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-qvt5q9o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qvt5q9o","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-k7dmpbl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-k7dmpbl","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"纪伯伦：不要因为走得太远而忘记为什么出发。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-xzns53p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xzns53p","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ku6er0w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ku6er0w","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用赏者贵信，用罚者贵必。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-hpomn5b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hpomn5b","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ei3upzn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ei3upzn","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"傲不可长，欲不可纵，乐不可极，志不可满。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5mb3y4v","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5mb3y4v","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-emohrus","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-emohrus","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子爱财，取之有道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-qe4alkr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qe4alkr","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-nrr7yoo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nrr7yoo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"余光中：敢在时间里自焚的人，必在永恒里结晶。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5jcrc7c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5jcrc7c","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-dpt3pw5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dpt3pw5","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"主不可以怒而兴师，将不可以愠而致战；合于利而动，不合于利而止。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-hjt6uu1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hjt6uu1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-hq4ba24","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hq4ba24","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵形象水，水之形，避高而趋下，兵之形，避实而击虚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-515897m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-515897m","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-33r6r4c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-33r6r4c","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海子：永远是这样，风后面是风，天空上面是天空，道路前面还是道路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-6yaq31h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-6yaq31h","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-vw6k5w3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vw6k5w3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：如果你抑郁了，说明你活在过去；如果你焦虑了，说明你活在未来；如果你平静了，才说明你活在现在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-hxbcdrp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hxbcdrp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-z9urffk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-z9urffk","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对愁人勿乐，对哭人勿笑，对失意人勿矜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-wfo619c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wfo619c","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-a717f07","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-a717f07","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知胜有五：知可以战与不可以战者胜，识众寡之用者胜，上下同欲者胜，以虞待不虞者胜，将能而君不御者胜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ixpk1l8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ixpk1l8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ea4tomm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ea4tomm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"钝学累功，不妨精熟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-m4usc0j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-m4usc0j","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-rehdjpq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rehdjpq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"闭门即是深山，读书随处净土。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-rndvgas","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rndvgas","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-uflj7qm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-uflj7qm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人非生而知之者，孰能无惑?惑而不从师，其为惑也，终不解矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-0tilu2p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0tilu2p","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-yz3ce7k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yz3ce7k","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"见胜不过众人之所知，非善之善者也；战胜而天下曰善，非善之善者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-cdu8m2n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-cdu8m2n","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-75tvl7o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-75tvl7o","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"折芦花赠远，零落一身秋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-b4sg9ol","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-b4sg9ol","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-k80l57q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-k80l57q","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老骥伏枥志千里，短锥处囊半寸锋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-d2x5xyj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-d2x5xyj","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-2tdzjma","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2tdzjma","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"只要厄运打不垮信念，希望之光就会驱散绝望之云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-9d7b61q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9d7b61q","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-2y6siwm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2y6siwm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"以势交者，势尽则疏，以利合者，利尽则散。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-mkzyy5u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-mkzyy5u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-li8y7sh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-li8y7sh","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如月之恒，如日之升。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-1d5bvtu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-1d5bvtu","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-zhzxwwa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-zhzxwwa","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"合军聚众，务在激气。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-bsd6h09","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bsd6h09","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-sbkm7y3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-sbkm7y3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贝尔纳：构成我们学习最大障碍的是已知的东西，而不是未知的东西。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-x43lqrf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-x43lqrf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ulfyqvv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ulfyqvv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"约瑟夫·海勒《第二十二条军规》：任何值得为它而死的东西，肯定值得为它而生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-mjsrebt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-mjsrebt","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-cdepyna","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-cdepyna","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"云路鹏程九万里，雪窗萤火二十年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-dazicbi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dazicbi","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3xx7jrg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3xx7jrg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"华而不实，怨之所聚也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-fo6hfjb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-fo6hfjb","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-vz2ae69","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vz2ae69","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"精卫衔微木，将以填沧海；刑天舞干戚，猛志固常在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5arydt4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5arydt4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ys8yk8s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ys8yk8s","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自知者不怨人，知命者不怨天；怨人者穷，怨天者无志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-891anic","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-891anic","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-u7bpdpm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-u7bpdpm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丹青不知老将至，富贵于我如浮云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-q4lumsd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-q4lumsd","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-w3eki9c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-w3eki9c","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"胡适：凡富于创造性的人必敏于模仿，凡不善于模仿的人决不能创造。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-0l6f17l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0l6f17l","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-bvl93c2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bvl93c2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"节义傲青云，文章高白雪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ax7zw84","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ax7zw84","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-uxh69n0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-uxh69n0","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提得起，放得下，算得到，做得完，看得破，撇得开。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-9c9ys39","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9c9ys39","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-rkopt3e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rkopt3e","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪曾祺：一定要爱着点什么，恰似草木对光阴的钟情。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-unkcqjm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-unkcqjm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-7g10vjv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7g10vjv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我有所念人，隔在远远乡。我有所感事，结在深深肠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-bgavmag","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bgavmag","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-cbgsfby","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-cbgsfby","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草不谢荣于春风，木不怨落于秋天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-datxxoz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-datxxoz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qb3um28","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qb3um28","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一竹一兰一石，有节有香有骨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-uds8273","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-uds8273","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-xhvqgud","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xhvqgud","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"笔落惊风雨，诗成泣鬼神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-cwlpeiw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-cwlpeiw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-43ckizs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-43ckizs","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"合抱之木，生于毫末；九层之台，起于累土；千里之行，始于足下。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-abayzba","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-abayzba","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-w3otqz6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-w3otqz6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山不让尘，川不辞盈。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-9fj4c44","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9fj4c44","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3p6mhd1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3p6mhd1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"皑如山上雪，皎若云间月。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-kyenx1i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kyenx1i","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ref3jx5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ref3jx5","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"客子光阴诗卷里，杏花消息雨声中。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-e62aac1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e62aac1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-eqbhjmn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-eqbhjmn","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：我们的眼睛就是我们的监狱，而目光所及之处就是监狱的围墙。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-078dn8f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-078dn8f","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-yfpewdf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yfpewdf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪中送炭人间少，锦上添花世上多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-c9brhln","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-c9brhln","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-7nbuhd6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7nbuhd6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"蒲柳之姿，望秋而落；松柏之质，经霜弥茂。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-nhhy396","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nhhy396","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-mn5s7nx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-mn5s7nx","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不戚戚于贫贱，不汲汲于富贵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-0dj2fbw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0dj2fbw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-9lbxm5o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9lbxm5o","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"门前红叶地，不扫待知音。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-rndhow5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rndhow5","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-wgyzhce","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wgyzhce","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"村上春树：这个世界上根本没有正确的选择，我们只不过是要努力奋斗，使当初的选择变得正确。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ukgf0yy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ukgf0yy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-orukwnp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-orukwnp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"缘木求鱼，煎水作冰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-7yliiwc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7yliiwc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3lbyus2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3lbyus2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苟日新，日日新，又日新。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-mi7n19m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-mi7n19m","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-d2a716s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-d2a716s","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贫无可奈惟求俭，拙亦何妨只要勤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-43vyuh8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-43vyuh8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-6l6d4hp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-6l6d4hp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文章千古事，得失寸心知。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-wf67t41","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wf67t41","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qo23per","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qo23per","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨滴能击穿石头，并不是下落的速度快，而是因为掉落在石头上的次数多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-dwfbekt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dwfbekt","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-r7mh4iv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-r7mh4iv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人有逆天之时，天无绝人之路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-7gewqxa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7gewqxa","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-m9fkgl1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-m9fkgl1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"宁为宇宙闲吟客，怕作乾坤窃禄人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-qqay90k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qqay90k","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-lmh3jdv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lmh3jdv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"受光于隙见一床，受光于窗见室央，受光于庭户见一堂，受光于天下照四方。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-wfuambb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wfuambb","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-pxtgkoe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-pxtgkoe","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马不可以服重，牛不可以追速。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-31r9ize","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-31r9ize","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-dxfkdy6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dxfkdy6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"改过不吝，从善如流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-xc7hbk1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xc7hbk1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qtyc2tf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qtyc2tf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚负凌云万丈才，一生襟抱未曾开。鸟啼花落人何在，竹死桐枯凤不来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-p096jc1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-p096jc1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-4brjdci","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-4brjdci","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兰生幽谷，不为莫服而不芳；舟在江海，不为莫乘而不浮；君子行义，不为莫知而止休。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-jr6du7h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-jr6du7h","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-rmg50sa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rmg50sa","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一日不思量，也攒眉千度。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-lw20mm6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lw20mm6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-u4v1uuf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-u4v1uuf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"彊弩之极，矢不能穿鲁缟；冲风之末，力不能漂鸿毛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-m5q53nh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-m5q53nh","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-2hnfqih","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2hnfqih","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时来天地皆同力，运去英雄不自由。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-zporrz8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-zporrz8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-e7ng5cy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e7ng5cy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"倒持干戈，授人以柄。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-nt4bbxo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nt4bbxo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-b1p3e8x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-b1p3e8x","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生一世，草生一春。来如风雨，去似微尘。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-p4fvt47","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-p4fvt47","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-jx6i8h5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-jx6i8h5","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪莱：未来不足惧，过往不须泣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-0s1mks6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0s1mks6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-pofgsg4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-pofgsg4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从善如登，从恶如崩。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-cm3tdm2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-cm3tdm2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-cjtog0c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-cjtog0c","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"春生、夏长、秋收、冬藏，天之正也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-uwlhgjf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-uwlhgjf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-s5otm4b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-s5otm4b","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前事不忘，后事之师。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-9h8ozse","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9h8ozse","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-c2x10b0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-c2x10b0","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"逢人不说人间事，便是人间无事人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-bep5x0g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bep5x0g","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-0yl2e17","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0yl2e17","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"花开花落树之常，能上能下人中强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-lyvvxro","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lyvvxro","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-dd07h0d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dd07h0d","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"立品同白玉，读书到青云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-u3zbakz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-u3zbakz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-sye6x70","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-sye6x70","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陀思妥耶夫斯基：爱具体的人，不要爱抽象的人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-9ntqex2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9ntqex2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qcbzpi4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qcbzpi4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凭君莫话封侯事，一将功成万骨枯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-seh1tt9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-seh1tt9","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-atlk1ho","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-atlk1ho","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天下皆知美之为美，斯恶已。皆知善之为善，斯不善已。有无相生，难易相成，长短相形，高下相盈，音声相和，前后相随，恒也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-vwm3jsy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vwm3jsy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ekey408","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ekey408","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子之心事，天青日白，不可使人不知；君子之才华，玉韫珠藏，不可使人易知。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-j5h36e7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-j5h36e7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-akswzl2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-akswzl2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"除掉荒草的最好办法，不是让除完草的土地荒着，而是种上庄稼。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-hiwdiyc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hiwdiyc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-fx88hoe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-fx88hoe","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善战者，求之于势，不责于人。故能择人而任势。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-goa56uh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-goa56uh","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-yit8q0c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yit8q0c","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"川泽纳污，所以成其深；山岳藏疾，所以就其大。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-hoqbzkt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hoqbzkt","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-fyex142","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-fyex142","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"覆水不可收，行云难重寻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-wt7cbjq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wt7cbjq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-bh8cvc5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-bh8cvc5","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相鼠有皮，人而无仪！人而无仪，不死何为？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-a5r6o0k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-a5r6o0k","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-e39xbuo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e39xbuo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为天地立心，为生民立命，为往圣继绝学，为万世开太平。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-esko4cr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-esko4cr","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-mceio4b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-mceio4b","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"狡兔死，走狗烹；飞鸟尽，良弓藏；敌国破，谋臣亡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-11pqkmh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-11pqkmh","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3ad808w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3ad808w","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马丁·路德·金：我们这一代人终将感到悔恨，不仅仅因为坏人的可憎言行，更因为好人的可怕沉默。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-kyy95i6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kyy95i6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-8etemsb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8etemsb","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我本将心向明月，奈何明月照沟渠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-vrg0m77","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vrg0m77","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-q4380au","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-q4380au","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"临渊羡鱼，不如退而结网；扬汤止沸，不如去火抽薪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-uxlabwp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-uxlabwp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qtjjudg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qtjjudg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"芳林新叶催陈叶，流水前波让后波。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-8568hum","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8568hum","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-z5w0tm6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-z5w0tm6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"日出扶桑一丈高，人间万事细如毛。野夫怒见不平处，磨损胸中万古刀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-d0ydicx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-d0ydicx","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3f3fo2g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3f3fo2g","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：果实的事业是尊贵的，花的事业是甜美的，但是让我做叶的事业吧，叶是谦逊地、专心地垂着绿荫的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-lu33gcr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lu33gcr","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-hep8cws","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-hep8cws","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子耻不修，不耻见污。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-x27sqpo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-x27sqpo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-35n3rlx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-35n3rlx","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陶行知：做学问就是要学要问。光学不问，只做到一半；光问不学，也只是一半。又学又问，才是完整的学问。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-a802b0t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-a802b0t","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-z9h9jyj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-z9h9jyj","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"恶不可积，过不可长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-f636zhe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-f636zhe","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-6ukh2cd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-6ukh2cd","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"众里嫣然通一顾，人间颜色如尘土。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-iw66nsk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-iw66nsk","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3m3yb5h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3m3yb5h","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将者，智、信、仁、勇、严也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-snsbcou","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-snsbcou","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-5wd5ulc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5wd5ulc","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老舍：才华是刀刃，辛苦是磨刀石。很锋利的刀刃，若日久不用石磨，也会生锈，成为废物。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-vreudmi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vreudmi","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-0yt8fh7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0yt8fh7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"少年侠气，交结五都雄。肝胆洞，毛发耸。立谈中，死生同。一诺千金重。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-e076vbj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e076vbj","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-auxev09","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-auxev09","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗曼·罗兰 ：一个人的绝对自由是疯狂，一个国家的绝对自由是混乱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-dth8j74","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-dth8j74","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3jaebjv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3jaebjv","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学然后知不足，教然后知困。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-rjs4ff7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-rjs4ff7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-o8wo4df","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-o8wo4df","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"记人之长，忘人之短。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-y3dtwg4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-y3dtwg4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-zj1bdwq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-zj1bdwq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知彼知己者，百战不殆；不知彼而知己，一胜一负，不知彼，不知己，每战必殆。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-h7ackfg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-h7ackfg","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-449t7r0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-449t7r0","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"月缺不改光，剑折不改刚。月缺魄易满，剑折铸复良。势利压山岳，难屈志士肠。男儿自有守，可杀不可苟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-m48cc4b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-m48cc4b","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-9lwvn2m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-9lwvn2m","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生贵相知，何必金与钱？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-3ba89q7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3ba89q7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qw0xx0n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qw0xx0n","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有真才者，必不矜才。有实学者，必不夸学。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-b44kq0s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-b44kq0s","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ljt14m8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ljt14m8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"薄我货者也，欲与我市者也；訾我行者，欲与我友者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ai73mm2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ai73mm2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-3ixw37j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-3ixw37j","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"风乍起，吹皱一池春水。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-jzg1cwy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-jzg1cwy","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-vzrt8p3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vzrt8p3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生万事须自为，跬步江山即寥廓。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-0x6h316","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0x6h316","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-v930hs0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-v930hs0","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"十年磨一剑，霜刃未曾试。今日把示君，谁有不平事？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-sei8xw6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-sei8xw6","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-pndgzgz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-pndgzgz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草木秋死，松柏独在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-y5xzk0y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-y5xzk0y","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-r6bz8g8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-r6bz8g8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生是一匹马，轻快而健壮的马。人，要像骑手那样大胆而细心地驾驭它。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-7wqpx2f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7wqpx2f","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-plopvz9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-plopvz9","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"水广者鱼大，山高者树修。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-4bi1wez","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-4bi1wez","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-n6dcb04","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-n6dcb04","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生如梦，把梦看得太认真，固然是个大傻瓜；但以为人生如梦，就以为不必认真，也是个头等大傻瓜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-4vwtfco","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-4vwtfco","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-d3a8za4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-d3a8za4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一叶浮萍归大海，为人何处不相逢！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-skx7y0i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-skx7y0i","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-v7fs5cs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-v7fs5cs","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"力田不如逢年，善仕不如遇合。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-y3j3hz3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-y3j3hz3","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-xqb1oiu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xqb1oiu","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道路难行钱作马，城池不克酒为兵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-8jrtlny","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-8jrtlny","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-m0ja3o7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-m0ja3o7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古人云，“读书百遍，其义自见”。谓读得熟，则不待解说，自晓其义也。余尝谓，读书有三到，谓心到，眼到，口到。心不在此，则眼不看仔细，心眼既不专一，却只漫浪诵读，决不能记，记亦不能久也。三到之中，心到最急。心既到矣，眼口岂不到乎？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-htkngs7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-htkngs7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-p92bxlf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-p92bxlf","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知人者智，自知者明。胜人者有力，自胜者强。知足者富。强行者有志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-oy9m1e7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-oy9m1e7","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-wdbnta8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-wdbnta8","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"驿寄梅花，鱼传尺素。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-783oa18","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-783oa18","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-382ot1e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-382ot1e","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自然既极博大，也极残忍，战胜一切，孕育众生。蝼蚁蚍蜉，伟人巨匠，一样在它怀抱中，和光同见。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-e9x8rkw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e9x8rkw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-qenfu56","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-qenfu56","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：与恶龙缠斗过久，自身亦成恶龙；凝视深渊过久，深渊将回以凝视。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ayab6is","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ayab6is","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-yu8pmuw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-yu8pmuw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天戴其苍，地履其黄，纵有千古，横有八荒，前途似海，来日方长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ptaz3kx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ptaz3kx","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-tjs7v8u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-tjs7v8u","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子坦荡荡，小人长戚戚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-pv0xwue","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-pv0xwue","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-u2frp6t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-u2frp6t","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"心中有丘壑，眉目作山河。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-2m1r76h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2m1r76h","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-99yqoox","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-99yqoox","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"寄蜉蝣于天地，渺沧海之一粟。哀吾生之须臾，羡长江之无穷。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-kmm3biq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kmm3biq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-2fm60fz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2fm60fz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"明代思想家袁了凡：昨日种种，譬如昨日死；今日种种，譬如今日生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-e69yf9a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e69yf9a","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-c0a8k53","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-c0a8k53","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"黑格尔：只有永远躺在泥坑里的人，才不会再掉进坑里。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-5s5yxxq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-5s5yxxq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-t489s0q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-t489s0q","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"子在齐闻《韶》，三月不知肉味，曰：‘不图为乐之至于斯也。’"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-ptcpx97","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ptcpx97","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-t5d6qvm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-t5d6qvm","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：命定的局限尽可永在，不屈的挑战却不可须臾或缺。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-nbhndn1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-nbhndn1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-g8rjvzk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-g8rjvzk","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：当我走向你的时候，我原想收获一缕春风，你却给了我整个春天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-q7rbpxo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-q7rbpxo","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-moyw81p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-moyw81p","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：我相信，在群星当中有一颗星星，引领我的生命，穿越不可知的黑暗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-62nuhg1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-62nuhg1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-kddw5pj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-kddw5pj","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：心晴的时候，雨也是晴；心雨的时候，晴也是雨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-pbdgg2s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-pbdgg2s","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-vt3cobw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vt3cobw","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"聂卫平：遇到顺势而下的时候，就一泻千里；遇到阻碍过不去的时候，就绕一下，但我的目标一直是向前走的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-x3rytv1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-x3rytv1","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-7fslzpr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-7fslzpr","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"曼德拉：我没有失败过。要么赢得胜利，要么学到东西。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-6lgmjy4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-6lgmjy4","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-e51by58","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e51by58","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间是单程车票，我们只能向前；而记忆是随身行李，始终伴你同行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-2fyce57","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-2fyce57","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-n0p08nz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-n0p08nz","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"喷泉之所以漂亮，是因为它有压力；瀑布之所以壮观，是因为它没有退路；滴水之所以能穿石，是因为它贵在坚持。一只站在树枝上的鸟，从不害怕树枝会断裂，因为它相信的不是树枝，而是它自己的翅膀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-fe9xp7t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-fe9xp7t","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-ongqzcp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-ongqzcp","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"追风赶月莫停留，平芜尽处是春山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-llxbz88","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-llxbz88","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-vkk7btk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vkk7btk","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苏轼《浣溪沙·游蕲水清泉寺》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-515u1jd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-515u1jd","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-lovcj3n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-lovcj3n","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朱敦儒《鹧鸪天·西都作》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-4dk3r9h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-4dk3r9h","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-464lmpq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-464lmpq","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杜甫《蜀相》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-0sx1b2q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-0sx1b2q","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-vmwistl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-vmwistl","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《忆秦娥》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-e49msj2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-e49msj2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-xdod49d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-xdod49d","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《上李邕》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-s6dmcih","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-s6dmcih","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605082558-18r49v2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-18r49v2","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陆游《金错刀行》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605082558-oxqva6o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605082558-oxqva6o","updated":"20260605082558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20